# ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.undetermined

**Case**

Geo-tracking accuracy is undetermined.

## Declaration

```swift
case undetermined
```

## Discussion

This value indicates that because the session has not completed visual localization, geo-tracking accuracy is indeterminate.

## Accuracies

- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.high**: Geo-tracking accuracy is high.
- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.low**: Geo-tracking accuracy is low.
- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.medium**: Geo-tracking accuracy is average.
